Key Features that Make Your Home Services Marketplace Stand Out

Home Services Marketplace with Advanced Search

Demandium’s strong search filters allow customers to quickly find the specific services they need, whether it’s a plumbing emergency or a routine lawn care appointment. Your customers can use this feature to narrow down their choices. You can save their time & frustration of finding the exact service from your on demand home service marketplace.

Smart Bidding Enabled Home Services Marketplace App

The smart bidding system lets home service providers bid on customer requests. This gives customers more home service options to choose from. It also encourages providers to offer quality services at competitive prices. In the on-demand home services marketplace, this system drives better service delivery & helps to maintain a fair marketplace.

Customized Requests through On Demand Home Services App

Customers often have specific home service related needs. For example, hardware & interior setup while installing home theatre may not fit into pre-defined categories of your on demand home services marketplace. With this feature, they can create customized requests to get exactly what they need leading to higher satisfaction & more referrals.

Sustain Customers On the Home Services Marketplace Platform

In the competitive home services industry, retaining customers is just as crucial as attracting new ones. Demandium helps sustain strong customer relationships & ensures a rewarding experience on your home services marketplace platform. It offers an integrated wallet and loyalty points, flexible payment options, and real-time communication and support.

Cross Platform On Demand Home Service Marketplace

Demandium's cross-platform performance is designed to ensure that your home services marketplace operates seamlessly on any device. It provides your customers with a consistent experience whether they use a desktop, tablet, or smartphone. No matter the device, your customers can easily access the listed home services & enjoy smooth browsing.

Search Analytics of Home Services Marketplace App

Understanding how customers search for services can provide valuable insights for optimizing your marketplace for services. Analyzing search data helps you to identify popular services and customer preferences. Both keyword and user search analytics help you align your offerings with demand, identify pain points, and make data-driven decisions.

Seamless 3rd Party Integration in Home Service Platform

Integrate third-party services such as social media, mail configurations, SMS notifications, storage connection, reCAPTCHA, Apple login, etc easily with your on demand home service marketplace software. These integrations not only enhance communication and security but also provide a smoother and more connected service for your customers.

Dynamic Features for Your On Demand Home Services Platform

Discover how Demandium's advanced features simplify the aspect every aspect of your on demand home services marketplace. Each solution is designed to bring efficiency & growth opportunities to your home service business.

  • Admin Panel

  • User App

  • Business Website

  • Provider App

  • Serviceman App

Admin Panel

Multiple Business Zones

Set up multiple business zones in various locations to offer targeted on demand home services. Easily onboard providers to specific zones, manage the status & control all operations centrally.

Service Management

Add, update, or remove - overall manage service categories and subcategories for each home service zone. You can also activate or deactivate each category according to your business needs.

Provider Management

Simply manage onboard requests, add new home service providers, and set up the withdrawal method. This simplifies handling withdrawal requests and transactions for providers.

Transaction Management

Access a detailed transaction list of your on demand home services marketplace with transaction IDs, types, stakeholder names & balances. Easily download the list in Excel format for your convenience.

Booking Management

From customized requests to canceled ones efficiently monitor and manage all booking requests on your home services marketplace and ensure a smooth booking system for both customers and providers.

Promotion Management

Create & manage various promotional campaigns effectively from one central place by offering discounts, coupons, wallet bonuses, different campaigns, advertisement opportunities, and banners.

Explore Admin Demo

User App

Easy Signup and Login

Quickly onboard customers with a hassle-free signup and login process. Whether they're new users or returning clients, the straightforward interface ensures easy access to all available home services.

Multi-Language Supported

Serve a diverse customer base with home services by making it easier for users to navigate and book services in their preferred language. This feature enhances user satisfaction and expands reach.

Guest Checkout

Offer convenient service booking without mandatory account creation. Guest checkout speeds up the booking process, reducing friction and encouraging more first-time users to complete their bookings.

Choose Favorite Provider

Users can select their preferred home service provider. If they don't have a specific choice, the system or admin can automatically match them with the best available provider nearby.

Refer and Earn

Incentivize users to refer your home services marketplace to others. With a referral program, users can earn rewards. It helps you grow your customer base while keeping existing users engaged.

Wallet & Loyalty Points

Enhance customer satisfaction with digital wallets and loyalty programs. Users can convert loyalty points to wallet money which encourages repeat business and increases customer retention.

Explore User App Demo

Business Website

Header Menu

The header menu provides easy access to essential sections of your home service marketplace for users to quickly navigate through services, privacy policies, contact information, and more.

Button & Links

Strategically placed CTA buttons and links guide users to key actions like booking services, downloading apps, or signing up. It enhances the user experience and drives conversions.

Service Showcase

Highlight your top home services with a dedicated showcase area, allowing potential customers to know about the services along with providers who might be interested in joining the marketplace.

Social Proof

Build trust with testimonials and reviews from satisfied customers and, mention the number of service providers showcasing the quality and reliability of your home service marketplace to new visitors.

About Us Page

Share your company info, brand story, mission, and values on the About Us page, connecting with users on a personal level and establishing credibility in the home service industry.

Legal Pages

Ensure transparency and compliance of your home service platform and reassure your customers with well-crafted legal pages, including terms and conditions and a privacy policy page.

Explore Website Demo

Provider App

Easy Registration

Service providers can quickly create a profile & list their services after admin approval. The simple process helps them get started on the platform & begin offering home services in their local area.

Bid for Custom Booking

Providers can place bids on custom service requests, giving them the flexibility to choose jobs that suit their expertise and schedule. It helps them optimize their workload and earnings.

Subscription List

Providers can browse through service categories & subcategories listed by the admin directly from the app’s menu to subscribe to specific home services they want to offer that match their expertise.

Live Chat

Facilitate direct chat support with admin, servicemen, and customers to ensure clarity & trust in service details. This leads to higher customer satisfaction in your on demand home marketplace.

Reports & Analytics

Providers use detailed reports and analytics to track their performance, balance, accounts payable, & receivable. They can make informed decisions to improve their home service offerings through this.

Business Settings

Providers have full control over their operations by managing permissions for their servicemen. They can easily enable or disable options such as allowing servicemen to cancel or edit bookings.

Explore Provider App Demo

Serviceman App

Interactive Dashboard

Provide an at-a-glance overview of all active bookings, upcoming bookings, and earnings. This feature helps servicemen efficiently manage their day-to-day activities in the home service marketplace.

Booking List

Servicemen can access a booking list that displays all assigned jobs, including detailed information about each home service request. This organized list ensures that no task is overlooked.

Multi-Language Support

With multi-language & RTL support, servicemen can navigate the app in their preferred language, and manage bookings. This feature is crucial for home service marketplaces operating in diverse regions.

Notification

Real-time notifications keep servicemen informed about new bookings, changes in schedules, or important updates. This ensures that they are always up-to-date and can respond promptly to any needs.

Change Booking Status

Servicemen can easily update the status of a booking - from accepted to completed. This feature streamlines the workflow, providing transparency to both customers and administrators.

Live Chat

The built-in live chat feature allows servicemen to communicate with customers, admin & providers for quick resolutions to any issues that may arise during a booking & enhance service quality.

Frequently Asked Questions

Here are some common questions we get about Demandium’s home services marketplace platform.

1. How does the on demand home marketplace model work?

The on demand home marketplace connects customers and service providers on one platform. Customers can easily book and pay for services, while providers manage and get paid—all in a streamlined system.

2. How secure is the home services marketplace app?

Our home services marketplace app Demandium is built with powerful security features to protect user data and transactions. It includes secure payment gateways, user authentication, and regular updates to ensure a safe and reliable platform for your business.

3. Can I customize the on demand home services app source code to suit my business needs?

Yes, our home service app source code is customizable to fit your business needs and any specific requirements.

4. How long does it take to launch a home services marketplace?

Using a pre-built solution like Demandium won't take long to set up. The time it takes mainly depends on how complex your project customization is. The less complex it is, the faster it can be launched.
